* James D. Wolfensohn and Andrew Kircher (2005) &quot;Voice for the World&#x27;s Poor: Selected Speeches and Writings of World Bank President James D. Wolfensohn, 1995–2005&quot;; . Collection of speeches, articles, memoranda and op-eds.
* James D. Wolfensohn (2010). &quot;A Global Life: My Journey among Rich and Poor, from Wall Street to the World Bank&quot;, p. 96. Pan MacMillan; 

